+    /// Perform hybrid search
+    ///
+    /// # Arguments
+    /// * `query_vector` - Query vector for semantic search
+    /// * `query_text` - Query text for keyword matching
+    /// * `k` - Number of results to return
+    /// * `vector_search_fn` - Function to perform vector similarity search
+    ///
+    /// # Returns
